{"tid":1126613,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女師傅幫大家占塔羅！","createTime":"2019-04-26T13:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T18:34:55.000Z","uid":62507,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d7799d0f8be7bfc49f3409b202b2f6d4a35408","tid":1126613,"uid":62507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"大家好，我叫女師傅，幫大家占下塔羅（其實係自己超迷戀幫人占<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢個AC係我同男師傅一齊用<br />\n男師傅就專長中式野，睇掌相紫微斗數<br />\n女師傅就專長西式野，星座塔羅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過今次就女師傅負責，塔羅問卜<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n問題背景最好愈詳細愈好，時間愈近期愈好<br />\n<br />\n感情問題<br />\n例如<br />\n同A咩關係，識左幾耐，想點樣<br />\n同A拍拖左一段時間，佢想分手，可以點<br />\n同A拍拖左一段時間，有第三介入，點好<br />\n<br />\n學業事業問題<br />\n例如<br />\nDSE結果如何<br />\nDSE預左炒粉，想問升學應該讀i大好？<br />\n有份新工請我，但舊工又好pay，做新工好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n其他問題都ok<br />\n<br />\n如果太私隱既野，你可以telegram我地問（請注明搵男師傅定女師傅）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同男師傅會響ig同fb不定期post 星相問卜既野，你有性趣就follow啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nig:YourFaceYourFateHK<br />\ntg:YourFaceYourFateHK<br />\nfb:Your Face Your Fate"},{"pid":"0583523022b0d5ac7b884787849faad7abdbb979","tid":1126613,"uid":248470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"之前有個師父睇感情都好準<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fengshuiryan.com/5/占算實錄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fengshuiryan.com%2F5%2F%E5%8D%A0%E7%AE%97%E5%AF%A6%E9%8C%84&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e3eba293\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fengshuiryan.com/5/占算實錄</a>"},{"pid":"2e07df0dd28337fcdf2ba28ab6bace04d8be1602","tid":1126613,"uid":153229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"名 ：SY<br />\n出生日期：1998，9，21<br />\n<br />\n想問學業<br />\n黎緊會唔會有學校收<br />\n<br />\n或者其他野你想提點我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ac946b37ec7e4cb9786b6ccdc6088d7c267121"